Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:06.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,During our battle with Oracion Seis, \NHappy and Wendy were captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To cure the poisoned, suffering Erza, we \Nneed the power of the Sky Dragon Slayer, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why we split up \Nand are searchin' for 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us, Happy, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:28.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's love and dreams and you it'll become magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:35.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:48.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of admired this powerful world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:53.19,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chock-full of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:59.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Frozen time has started to move again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:05.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:11.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were we born? Why do we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:16.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any complicated answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:22.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh! Cry! Be honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:27.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple feelings are the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:35.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You can change those tears shed on sad nights into strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:42.53,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:03.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He once infiltrated the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:15.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show them just how scary we, \NNaked Mummy, can be, Zatou-niisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get them, real quick like, Gatou-niisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:30.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... We'll show them just how scary \Nwe, Naked Mummy, can be, Zatou-niisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:33.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that already, Gatou-niisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:36.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I, Zatou-niisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll show them just how...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'em, you lugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:46.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure got an earful of their \Nbrain-dead brother banter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:48.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like they're both \Nthe older brother, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a load of my magic shotgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,*twinkle*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:28.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't half bad, Zatou-niisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:31.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we take 'em on together, Gatou-niisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:37.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Girl and the Ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:50.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is... Jellal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal... That Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Jellal too, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy tried to kill \NErza and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:05.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And he used the Council to fire Etherion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I heard about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:11.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is a ghost, haunted by ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A wretched idealist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:22.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you owe him your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry and resurrect this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Whatever you do, \Ndon't resurrect that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not resurrect him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cure him. It should be simple for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:14.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal is a bad guy! He's \Ngonna steal Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so... I was saved by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was dear to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:40.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard rumors that he did bad things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't believe them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? We \Nwere right there when...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal would never do things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Give me some time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... This is real bad... \NHurry up and get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:27.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Mummy was beaten by just two wizards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:32.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me... \NNaked Mummy was beaten by just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that already, Gatou-niisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with these guys? They \Nweren't small fry at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they actually had some fight in 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they do! They're an entire guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world were you people thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, blabber-ape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your base?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't tellin' you, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, big-ape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are crazy, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guest, the rest is up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:10.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, flame-brain \Nbrat! Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:15.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really owe you for what you \Ndid to me way back when...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:18.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:23.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey ya, you breezy bastard! Long time indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it hangin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't got that kinda relationship, bub!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a hint, sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:33.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the guy responsible for trying to use \NLullaby to assassinate Gramps and the other Masters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:38.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to recall I beat the crap out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After the destruction of Eisenwald,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:46.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wandered as a free agent through the\Nguilds associated with Oracion Seis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The day I get revenge on you flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The day the Death God is born once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A revenge match? Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You people are going to fight more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:05.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more than just crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Air Magic, Aerial!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:11.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are getting cloudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears are ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lowered the oxygen content \Nin the air around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should no longer be able to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got such a cute face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play with 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to make me angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow Magic: Whiteout!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll steal your visibility, \Nand freeze your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:42.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-S-S-Strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Lamia Scale...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you a thing or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pict Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unison Pict!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, they're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick their butts, Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wood Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Owwy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel bad now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's perfect...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While they're distracted by \Nour cute little goblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unison Pict!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:32.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A wyvern?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They can even make something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is some skillful sketching!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, wyvern!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush the official guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:44.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockiron Spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:49.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon! Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doll Attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Snow Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rock Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Invocation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockiron Powder Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So much for our wyvern!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it even matter what we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:18.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they be fake, I cannot admire \Nthose that use living things so thoughtlessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:38.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive... Those monkeys \Nwere nothing compared to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:39.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:40.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:49.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Isn't wind the \Nworst match-up for flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to the elements, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:54.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time they fought it \Nwas a pretty tough battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but Natsu isn't the same as he was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this guy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:05.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical power... Compared to \Nbefore, it's on a whole other level!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! You've improved quite a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:10.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout this, Erigor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:18.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I gotta crush you pretty soon so I \Ncan get on with finding Happy and Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:21.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talkin' like that'll \Nbe so easy, you damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chop you to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Emera Baram!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that destructive power?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been playing around either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been training to build up my magic \Npower to get revenge on you ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:49.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:54.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge, again? You're always so obsessed \Nwith little stuff like that, Erigor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:12:00.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... There's got to be some \Nother reason that gets you fired up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:11.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about Eisenwald \Nor Oracion Seis anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:15.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I am a lone wizard, I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Wind Palm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:34.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blazing Fire Dragon Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:43.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm no match...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have finished that \Na bit faster, flame-brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good going there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power of Salamander?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:13:00.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Where are Happy and Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:02.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your base?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:11.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The abandoned village to the west? \NThe village of the ancients?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug their own grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They thought they would beat us, but ended \Nup revealing the location of their base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon, Sherry... Head to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Jura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense a great magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Oracion Seis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will engage them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:36.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I'll let you \Noff with this for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should feel lucky \Nto be alive, young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So... please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you shut it, you old fart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only 29!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you to shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:55.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be serious this time... So \Nlet's have a fair fight, man to man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young people these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... may have underestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see... When I'm not in front of \Na woman, I can't really fight for real...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, a skilled hawk should \Nhide its talons and all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, little pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to bring this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we just off him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:19.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should listen to your superiors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:22.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel-sama forgot to extract some info.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That copying magic I've heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's carry this guy there, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:35.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy! Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! There might be enemies here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Racer. Do not let them near.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:57.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:18.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lost Magic, Healing Magic... If \Nyou won't use it now, when would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:22.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle things here. \NYou hurry and go, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll let you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Charles, now's our chance! Wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... Get going on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:56.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped my running.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked more like you \Ntripped and fell to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you motion sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:18.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle you all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:44.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...hell is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:00.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:12.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. The poison seems \Nto be spreading more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki, have they found Wendy yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I can't contact anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact them... I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:56.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This person... saved my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:01.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy! You used Healing Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:04.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking? If you \Nuse that power recklessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tremendous magical power as always, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Jellal go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who that guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't bringing Wendy back with \Nyou more important right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to save Erza, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:19.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That did not go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:38.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is my mistake for releasing \Nhim from the restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:45.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's never been hostile toward me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:51.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he have overheard the discussions \Nabout Nirvana, even as he was sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Jellal intend to take \NNirvana for himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:57.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:59.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not hand it over to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal has escaped! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:10.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana should be where he is heading!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. I heard ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:16.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've already heard Jellal's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible speed this bastard has.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My codename is Racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster than anyone. Faster than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:33.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And all I do is run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:38.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He saved them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Brain should have been inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By beating him up, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:49.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy! Charles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Rampart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you... I'd get this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just used too much magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:32.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't getting past here, \Nnot even over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:37.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! To where Erza is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:46.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna save Erza, you bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn straight you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:55.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped my running twice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:57.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it won't be the last time, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice can even stop the time of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll never be able \Nto catch up, for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll always be eating \Nthe dust of Fairy Tail. {not exactly literal...}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:59.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Gray! He's totally \Nhogging all the cool parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:00.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.76,0:24:06.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray was thinking about \Nus when he stayed behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:09.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick and tired of him acting all cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.36,0:24:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:13.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he even listen to a word I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Dead Grand Prix
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:19.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what if it's over \Nby the time we get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:22.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case I guess I'll \Njust have to fight Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.53,0:24:24.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to always be that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:26.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
